Subject: Referral of Unresolved Customer Grievances for Further Investigation

Dear [Recipient/Department Name],

I am writing to formally refer the following unresolved customer grievances to your department for further investigation and resolution. Despite our initial efforts, these issues remain outstanding and require specialized attention.

Please find attached a summary of each case, including relevant details and previous actions taken. We kindly request your prompt review and appropriate follow-up with the customers involved.

Should you require any additional information or support from our team, please do not hesitate to contact me directly.

Thank you for your attention to these matters.

Best regards,

[Your Name]  
Senior Customer Service Representative  
[Your Contact Information]
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
